eu_initiatives: SAIS intends to participate in the European Commission's High Level Expert Group on Artificial Intelligence (https://ec.europa.eu/digital-single-market/en/news/call-high-level-expert-group-artificial-intelligence)
subsection: Non-governmental organisations, platforms and networks and similar
goals__remit: The purpose of the Swedish AI Association is to promote research, education and application of artificial intelligence in Sweden.
relevant_communication: SAIS is responsible for organizing the SAIS Workshop, the annual Swedish AI workshop. We are also organizing IJCAI-ECAI-2018 the International Joint Conference on AI and the European Conference on AI in Stockholm.
